原代码：
 _event.zrenderX = touch.clientX - root.offsetLeft
                                          ＋ document.body.scrollLeft;
 _event.zrenderY = touch.clientY - root.offsetTop
                                          ＋ document.body.scrollTop;

修改后代码：
 _event.zrenderX = touch.clientX - root.offsetLeft
                                          - document.body.scrollLeft;
 _event.zrenderY = touch.clientY - root.offsetTop
                                          - document.body.scrollTop;

